You can find a lot of documentation about this project in "docs" folder. Feel free to read them as needed. Start with [index.md](mdc:docs/index.md)

For Next.js projects, create page components under `components` folder instead of `app`. Files in `app` should only import/export components from `components`. Page components should be name like `HomePage`, `HomeLayout` etc. to improve searchability.

When you work in a branch which has name that starts with "ai/", use `./scripts/pr.sh` to create a PR for it.
